experiment_info.name: simulation_result_caching
experiment_info.description: Cache simulation results to eliminate redundant evaluations during CMA-ES
experiment_info.hypothesis: LRU cache on simulation results could eliminate redundant evaluations and speed up optimization

tuning_runs.notes: 10% cache hit rate, but overhead outweighs savings - SLOWER than baseline

result: FAILED - Caching overhead (22% slower) outweighs 10% cache hit savings. CMA-ES generates unique positions each iteration.
